Description: TMJOs text editor with full session persistence
 TMJPad is the native TMJOs text editor — no plugins, no syntax
 highlighting, just multiple tabs and total session persistence.
 .
 Closing the window saves the state of every tab (including unsaved
 ones); reopening restores everything exactly as it was. Auto-save
 of buffers happens on every modification (debounced 500ms), so
 crashes and forced kills never lose content.
 .
 Features:
   * Multiple tabs (Ctrl+N / Ctrl+W / Ctrl+Tab)
   * Total session persistence with atomic writes
   * Find & Replace (Ctrl+F / Ctrl+H)
   * Dark theme only, JetBrains Mono font
   * GTK4 + libadwaita native

